Commands:

* (PORTED, UI, add menu entry) quit: Quit the emulator
* (PORTED, PANEL, add shortuct key?) cycle: Execute one instruction at IC
* help: Print help
* (PORTED, UI) regs: Show user registers
* (PORTED, UI) sregs: Show system registers
* (PORTED, PANEL) clear: CPU clear (reset)
* (PORTED, UI) dasm: Disassembler
* (PORTED, UI) mem: Show memory contents
* (PORTED, PANEL) binload: Initiate binary load
* load: Load memory image from file
* memcfg: Show memory configuration
* memdump: Dump memory contents into a file
* brk: Manipulate breakpoints
* (PORTED, PANEL) start: Start emulation
* (PORTED, PANEL) stop: Stop emulation
* stk: Show stack
* log: Manipulate logging
* watch: Manipulate expression watches
* decode: Decode memory structures
* find: Search memory for a value


